{"tid":1745722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"救護員毋需展示名牌","createTime":"2019-11-22T11:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T12:10:08.000Z","uid":90199,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3a04df3bd3fbad7bb84e3aea78888d6ea0791927","tid":1745722,"uid":90199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"背景資料：救護員既日常工作制服要貼上自己既名牌，同消防員唔同。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DWkcg3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDWkcg3b.jpg&h=5fed81fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家見到冇名牌既救護員唔好以為係黑警扮，只係部門唔知做咩事出咁既指引，其實光明正大驚咩俾人知你叫咩名，而家收埋個名仲大嫌疑啦。"},{"pid":"180e6fcd4d5450486b887f9408587f0daa79a2c5","tid":1745722,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:16:53.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣反而驚警甴扮救護<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcqWt03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcqWt03.jpg&h=21ff8a84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd945963834a8b5eadc7dbf62f1feab712f0c69a","tid":1745722,"uid":215284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"擺明為咗掩護更多狗「喬裝」救護"},{"pid":"563d5067818e19a0d7aa059cc051af2a0253bff2","tid":1745722,"uid":90199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"咁樣搞到前線救護員更加難做，戴左以示清白又驚俾人話唔跟部門指示，唔戴面對市民又擔心被誤會係狗cosplay救護員"},{"pid":"b785797e6ff96e6efc81ed11e79d395f86199734","tid":1745722,"uid":132467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:37:50.000Z","msg":"關唔關 黑警著救護橙褸事呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n名正言順黑警可扮任何人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f213d43edb19fca34ce06a1a0364ba3916fc9f57","tid":1745722,"uid":270798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"唔理指引，照良心做，差佬問就話十幾年都有戴名牌，習慣左。"},{"pid":"2e740addfec8198ad214b96983a8ff7578d73bce","tid":1745722,"uid":270798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"係不&ldquo;需要&rdquo;，唔係不&ldquo;可以&rdquo;，即係你戴名牌佢吹你唔漲。"},{"pid":"31cbaf447986b26151ea779ccef7c1dd3d07f98f","tid":1745722,"uid":90199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e740addfec8198ad214b96983a8ff7578d73bce","tid":1745722,"uid":270798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"係不&ldquo;需要&rdquo;，唔係不&ldquo;可以&rdquo;，即係你戴名牌佢吹你唔漲。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:57:55.000Z","msg":"最後都會話為左整體嘅一致性，全部人唔俾戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a2a8a660906674209d17778b17a9309b4128f9","tid":1745722,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd945963834a8b5eadc7dbf62f1feab712f0c69a","tid":1745722,"uid":215284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"擺明為咗掩護更多狗「喬裝」救護"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"2899a468c60ee68342a0913dc5db57f7b4d6935d","tid":1745722,"uid":270619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"180e6fcd4d5450486b887f9408587f0daa79a2c5","tid":1745722,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:16:53.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣反而驚警甴扮救護<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcqWt03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcqWt03.jpg&h=21ff8a84&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"save<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfacd193fe7e7bb186ad4a0ffb638acb25ba0f6","tid":1745722,"uid":313307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:03:50.000Z","msg":"咁簡單啦，唔戴名牌就唔認佢係救護，唔好開路俾佢。黃救護怕咩show名牌"},{"pid":"0ff5c768aac1af0337bf0a57779025e0439d7e66","tid":1745722,"uid":2